---
title: Double Quick Sweet-Soy Chicken & Broccoli Noodles with Crispy Shallots
description: Chicken and noodles - it’s one of those epic comfort-food combos that always goes down a treat. This meal is full of savoury Asian flavours, with sweet soy seasoning on the chicken and Korean stir-fry sauce stirred through the noodles and veggies. Add a sprinkle of crispy shallots for a touch of crunch and dig in!
